WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.669
Hey, good morning family! I'm excited to

00:00:02.679 --> 00:00:04.550
be with y'all today. I have some things

00:00:04.560 --> 00:00:07.349
on my heart. First off, I want to say

00:00:07.359 --> 00:00:10.749
thank you for almost 100,000 subscribers.

00:00:10.759 --> 00:00:14.390
We are 3,000 people away from hitting

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:16.870
100,000 subs and I just want to tell you

00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:18.510
all thank you from the bottom of my

00:00:18.510 --> 00:00:18.520
heart,

00:00:18.520 --> 00:00:20.269
and my family thanks you. Thank

00:00:20.279 --> 00:00:21.950
you, thank you, God bless you all for

00:00:21.960 --> 00:00:24.109
supporting this channel and clicking the

00:00:24.119 --> 00:00:26.230
like button, the notifications, and making

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:28.910
comments down below. You are really truly

00:00:28.920 --> 00:00:30.470
getting the gospel

00:00:30.480 --> 00:00:32.990
spread throughout the world by doing

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.670
this. We are reaching souls

00:00:35.680 --> 00:00:37.190
every single day. I mean, we're getting

00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:39.030
somebody saved, somebody's getting

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:41.150
touched by the power of God, and I just

00:00:41.160 --> 00:00:42.990
want to say thank you. But if you could

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:44.990
today, please click that notification

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:47.510
bell, our little notification bell, and

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:50.470
then click the like button. We appreciate

00:00:50.470 --> 00:00:50.480
you

00:00:50.480 --> 00:00:52.510
clicking that like button. Click the

00:00:52.520 --> 00:00:54.990
subscribe button, and we just want to say

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:57.229
thank you for helping us

00:00:57.239 --> 00:00:58.950
spread the word, spread the gospel,

00:00:58.960 --> 00:01:00.990
because every time you do it helps get

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:03.270
us further in the YouTube algorithms.

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:05.030
I'm going to say

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:07.550
this, and I'm not attacking any

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:10.670
denomination or belief, okay? But I was

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:13.350
driving down the road and the Lord spoke

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:15.429
to me. Like I do, I pray a lot when I'm

00:01:15.439 --> 00:01:17.310
driving. I passed a Church of Jesus Christ of

00:01:17.320 --> 00:01:20.469
Latter-day Saints, LDS. I passed it; it

00:01:20.479 --> 00:01:24.069
was on my right, and

00:01:24.079 --> 00:01:26.590
instantaneously I

00:01:26.600 --> 00:01:28.830
started seeing in the spirit. I

00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:32.870
saw a honey glow coming into

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:35.469
that church and the Lord said to me,

00:01:35.479 --> 00:01:38.990
'Brandon, I'm bringing a great revival

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:42.109
into the LDS

00:01:42.109 --> 00:01:42.119
churches.'And

00:01:42.119 --> 00:01:44.389
he said, 'Brandon, there's going to be

00:01:44.399 --> 00:01:47.789
a separation from the doctrine of

00:01:47.799 --> 00:01:51.709
what they have

00:01:51.719 --> 00:01:53.550
believed.'Because

00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:55.310
I believe the Church of Jesus Christ of

00:01:55.320 --> 00:01:58.469
Latter-day Saints has an

00:01:58.469 --> 00:01:58.479
occult

00:01:58.479 --> 00:02:00.389
following to

00:02:00.389 --> 00:02:00.399
it,

00:02:00.399 --> 00:02:03.109
and I believe they're good people, so I

00:02:03.119 --> 00:02:04.630
don't want to offend anybody. If

00:02:04.640 --> 00:02:06.350
you're Latter-day

00:02:06.350 --> 00:02:06.360
Saint

00:02:06.360 --> 00:02:07.590
and you're watching this, I'm not trying

00:02:07.600 --> 00:02:08.869
to offend you, but I'm trying to

00:02:08.879 --> 00:02:10.869
tell you some of your beliefs

00:02:10.879 --> 00:02:14.229
I personally believe are way off. But the

00:02:14.239 --> 00:02:17.670
Lord said to me that he was going to

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:20.589
bring a great revival in the Church of Jesus Christ of

00:02:20.599 --> 00:02:22.190
Latter-day Saints and that there was

00:02:22.200 --> 00:02:24.830
going to be a changing of the tides.

00:02:24.840 --> 00:02:26.949
That's a good way to say a changing of

00:02:26.959 --> 00:02:28.910
things, and that there would be a people

00:02:28.920 --> 00:02:31.990
break off that were already in that, and

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:34.229
they would break off and there would be

00:02:34.239 --> 00:02:36.910
a great revival, a harvest of souls with

00:02:36.920 --> 00:02:39.149
some of these people. Not saying every

00:02:39.159 --> 00:02:41.869
church is going to do this, but the Lord

00:02:41.879 --> 00:02:44.430
said, 'I'm going to personally visit

00:02:44.440 --> 00:02:46.869
people and there's going to be a great

00:02:46.879 --> 00:02:49.750
manifestation of my glory upon those

00:02:49.750 --> 00:02:49.760
people.'And

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:52.110
he said, 'Brandon, I wish that

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:54.309
none should perish but all come to

00:02:54.319 --> 00:02:56.790
repentance and to know me

00:02:56.790 --> 00:02:56.800
personally.'I'm

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:58.990
telling you all, there's

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:01.509
going to be a great move of God in the

00:03:01.519 --> 00:03:03.830
Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints.

00:03:03.830 --> 00:03:03.840
I

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:06.430
saw some correction, some

00:03:06.440 --> 00:03:09.149
bondages being broken off of people, and

00:03:09.159 --> 00:03:10.990
there's going to be some great liberty

00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:13.710
and some great spiritual freedom

00:03:13.720 --> 00:03:15.270
coming to some folks in that

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:17.350
denomination of people. Then

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:19.309
another thing: the other night I

00:03:19.319 --> 00:03:21.670
was praying and the Lord opened my ears

00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:23.229
up in the spirit realm and I heard two

00:03:23.239 --> 00:03:24.910
angels talking. It was a lot of

00:03:24.920 --> 00:03:26.589
personal things that were going on in my

00:03:26.599 --> 00:03:28.270
house, and I'm not going to go into a lot

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:32.789
of that, but what inspired me

00:03:32.799 --> 00:03:37.070
to

00:03:37.080 --> 00:03:40.750
tell you all is part of what the angel said.

00:03:40.760 --> 00:03:42.710
The two angels were talking; they

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:45.509
were watching over my family and the

00:03:45.519 --> 00:03:47.229
Lord allowed me to hear the guardian

00:03:47.239 --> 00:03:49.110
angels. They were having a

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:51.229
conversation and one angel

00:03:51.239 --> 00:03:53.710
said to the other, 'What he

00:03:53.720 --> 00:03:56.350
does not know, and what he needs

00:03:56.360 --> 00:03:58.470
to know,

00:03:58.480 --> 00:04:03.309
is how important is

00:04:03.309 --> 00:04:03.319
his

00:04:03.319 --> 00:04:06.830
love walk. Where is his

00:04:06.830 --> 00:04:06.840
love walk?'The

00:04:06.840 --> 00:04:09.630
things you'll be judged upon

00:04:09.640 --> 00:04:12.309
the most when you get to the other side,

00:04:12.319 --> 00:04:14.229
the things that the Lord is weighing

00:04:14.239 --> 00:04:17.870
most, is what did you do with love? It was

00:04:17.880 --> 00:04:20.509
so important. I want you to understand

00:04:20.519 --> 00:04:24.430
this: the angels were talking and he said,

00:04:24.440 --> 00:04:26.469
'What did you do with

00:04:26.479 --> 00:04:28.749
love, Brandon?'That's what the Lord's

00:04:28.759 --> 00:04:30.270
going to ask. 'Brandon,

00:04:30.280 --> 00:04:31.990
I wonder if

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:35.110
he knows this yet.'It was amazing

00:04:35.120 --> 00:04:36.990
because I'm hearing this in the spirit

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:41.110
and he said, 'What did he do with love?

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:43.469
Where is his love

00:04:43.479 --> 00:04:47.590
walk? How did he operate in love on the

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:49.870
earth towards his wife and to his

00:04:49.880 --> 00:04:52.189
children and to those that are around

00:04:52.189 --> 00:04:52.199
him?'That

00:04:52.199 --> 00:04:55.670
was the most important

00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:58.550
thing that he would ever operate

00:04:58.560 --> 00:05:00.230
in.

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:03.270
When I heard the angel talking, I

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:05.790
froze and I just got quiet and I thought

00:05:05.800 --> 00:05:08.270
about what the angel was

00:05:08.280 --> 00:05:11.590
saying. 'What did he do with

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:14.749
love? What did he do with love?'I woke up

00:05:14.749 --> 00:05:14.759
the next day and

00:05:14.759 --> 00:05:19.230
I told my wife,

00:05:19.240 --> 00:05:23.629
'Hey honey,

00:05:23.639 --> 00:05:25.110
this is what I heard two angels talking

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:28.070
about last night.'And she said, 'Brandon, my

00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:29.950
favorite passage of scripture even

00:05:29.960 --> 00:05:33.230
growing up as a teenager was

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:36.309
1 Corinthians

00:05:36.309 --> 00:05:36.319
13.'It

00:05:36.319 --> 00:05:39.110
goes through

00:05:41.000 --> 00:05:42.629
the love chapter. It's

00:05:42.639 --> 00:05:44.550
beautiful. My wife's talking right now,

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:46.390
you can hear she's talking about how this is

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:47.870
her favorite; she read it

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:49.110
over and over again. Because she

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:51.550
would always ask as a

00:05:51.560 --> 00:05:54.110
teenager, 'What does it take to

00:05:54.120 --> 00:05:56.990
be a good Christian? What does it take to

00:05:57.000 --> 00:05:59.710
be a person that is walking with

00:05:59.710 --> 00:05:59.720
Jesus?'And

00:05:59.720 --> 00:06:03.070
the Lord spoke to my wife and

00:06:03.080 --> 00:06:04.110
he told

00:06:04.120 --> 00:06:07.510
her, 'Somebody that walks in

00:06:07.520 --> 00:06:10.790
love and operates in the full measure of

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:13.029
love as a Christian.'So if you look

00:06:13.039 --> 00:06:17.550
at

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:21.550
1 Corinthians

00:06:21.560 --> 00:06:25.110
13 and you go through it—come sit by me—1 Corinthians 13:

00:06:25.110 --> 00:06:25.120
'Love is not bragging.'This is Diana again, you all know. It

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:27.350
goes through there and

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:36.070
talks about love and all the things that

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:37.909
love is. Love is

00:06:37.919 --> 00:06:40.749
not bragging, it does not boast,

00:06:40.759 --> 00:06:43.110
it does not take account

00:06:43.110 --> 00:06:43.120
of

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:45.510
a suffered wrong, it does all things.

00:06:45.520 --> 00:06:47.870
It's beautiful, everything that

00:06:47.880 --> 00:06:50.430
it's saying in 1 Corinthians 13.

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:54.070
I've read it over and over

00:06:54.070 --> 00:06:54.080
again.

00:06:54.080 --> 00:06:56.430
My attempt is to memorize

00:06:56.440 --> 00:06:58.029
the whole

00:06:58.039 --> 00:07:00.670
chapter because when I heard the angel, I

00:07:00.670 --> 00:07:00.680
realized

00:07:00.680 --> 00:07:03.469
nothing else will really matter. The

00:07:03.479 --> 00:07:05.350
thing that will matter the

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:09.189
most is what did you do with love? How

00:07:09.199 --> 00:07:11.390
did you love your wife? How did you love

00:07:11.400 --> 00:07:13.469
your children? How did you treat them in

00:07:13.479 --> 00:07:15.990
love? Did you honor them? Did you treat

00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:18.270
them with respect? Did you do 1

00:07:18.280 --> 00:07:20.430
Corinthians

00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:24.390
13? I wept the next morning because I'm not

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:26.749
always the nicest person. I'm cranky a

00:07:26.749 --> 00:07:26.759
lot—cranky

00:07:26.759 --> 00:07:28.990
to her, cranky to the kids

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:30.710
sometimes, just with the

00:07:30.720 --> 00:07:32.629
pressures of life. I'm not giving an excuse

00:07:32.629 --> 00:07:32.639
for

00:07:32.639 --> 00:07:34.430
it, but I'm just telling you all, it's

00:07:34.440 --> 00:07:36.670
just

00:07:36.680 --> 00:07:39.309
real. What did you do with

00:07:39.319 --> 00:07:42.430
love? When I heard the

00:07:42.440 --> 00:07:45.790
angel say that, it pierced

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:50.029
me. It still pierces me because I think

00:07:50.039 --> 00:07:54.710
about how I lack so much in that.

00:07:54.720 --> 00:07:56.629
Nothing else

00:07:56.639 --> 00:07:58.830
matters: prophecy, just like she was

00:07:58.840 --> 00:08:00.390
talking about,

00:08:00.400 --> 00:08:04.950
the gifts of the spirit, faith,

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:07.670
hope, and love. But the greatest of these

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:10.990
is love. There's more to this; it

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:13.550
says God is

00:08:13.560 --> 00:08:16.309
love.

00:08:16.319 --> 00:08:19.629
So whenever the angel was saying

00:08:19.639 --> 00:08:21.629
that, 'What did he do with love?

00:08:21.639 --> 00:08:25.149
Does he know what he's going

00:08:25.159 --> 00:08:27.110
to be asked? What did he do with love on

00:08:27.120 --> 00:08:27.790
the

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:31.350
earth? How did he treat other

00:08:31.350 --> 00:08:31.360
people?'Not

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:34.350
how did they treat you and

00:08:34.360 --> 00:08:37.070
how you respond; you respond in

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:39.469
love. Love takes no account of

00:08:39.469 --> 00:08:39.479
a

00:08:39.479 --> 00:08:42.949
suffered wrong. When people do you wrong,

00:08:42.959 --> 00:08:46.310
love is not jealous, it is not envious, it

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:49.150
doesn't brag, it's not boastful. So I'm

00:08:49.160 --> 00:08:53.150
going to have Diana read 1 Corinthians

00:08:53.160 --> 00:08:56.870
13, because the bottom line is, if we're not

00:08:56.880 --> 00:09:00.710
practicing this right here—prophecy, any

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:03.350
of this stuff—it doesn't matter if we

00:09:03.360 --> 00:09:05.790
are not walking in the love of God with

00:09:05.800 --> 00:09:08.310
people, treating people with respect,

00:09:08.320 --> 00:09:09.949
honoring them, doing this verse that

00:09:09.959 --> 00:09:12.790
she's fixing to read to you.

00:09:12.800 --> 00:09:14.550
'Though I speak

00:09:14.560 --> 00:09:17.150
with the tongues of men and of angels,

00:09:17.160 --> 00:09:20.030
but have not love, I have become sounding

00:09:20.040 --> 00:09:23.069
brass or a clanging cymbal. And though I

00:09:23.079 --> 00:09:25.389
have the gift of prophecy and understand

00:09:25.399 --> 00:09:27.910
all mysteries and all knowledge,

00:09:27.920 --> 00:09:30.790
and though I have all faith so that

00:09:30.800 --> 00:09:33.150
I could remove mountains, but have not

00:09:33.160 --> 00:09:36.590
love, I am nothing. And though I bestow

00:09:36.600 --> 00:09:39.030
all my goods to feed the poor, and though

00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:42.069
I give my body to be burned, but have not

00:09:42.079 --> 00:09:45.910
love, it profits me nothing. Love suffers

00:09:45.920 --> 00:09:49.630
long and is kind; love does not envy; love

00:09:49.640 --> 00:09:52.430
does not parade itself, it is not puffed

00:09:52.440 --> 00:09:55.870
up; does not behave rudely, does not seek

00:09:55.880 --> 00:09:59.910
its own, is not provoked, thinks no

00:09:59.920 --> 00:10:03.630
evil; does not rejoice in iniquity, but

00:10:03.640 --> 00:10:07.389
rejoices in the truth; bears all things,

00:10:07.399 --> 00:10:10.910
believes all things, hopes all things,

00:10:10.920 --> 00:10:15.430
endures all things. Love

00:10:15.440 --> 00:10:17.350
never fails. But whether there are

00:10:17.360 --> 00:10:20.110
prophecies, they will fail; whether there

00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:23.150
are tongues, they will cease; whether

00:10:23.160 --> 00:10:26.030
there is knowledge, it will vanish away.

00:10:26.040 --> 00:10:28.750
For we know in part and we prophesy in

00:10:28.760 --> 00:10:29.630
part.

00:10:29.640 --> 00:10:32.350
But when that which is perfect has

00:10:32.360 --> 00:10:34.910
come, then that which is in part will be

00:10:34.920 --> 00:10:35.750
done

00:10:35.760 --> 00:10:38.750
away. When I was a child, I spoke as a

00:10:38.760 --> 00:10:41.509
child, I understood as a child, I thought

00:10:41.519 --> 00:10:44.550
as a child; but when I became a man, I put

00:10:44.560 --> 00:10:48.030
away childish things. For now we see in a

00:10:48.040 --> 00:10:52.150
mirror dimly, but then face to face. Now I

00:10:52.160 --> 00:10:55.629
know in part, but then I shall know just

00:10:55.639 --> 00:11:00.069
as I also am known. And now abide faith,

00:11:00.079 --> 00:11:03.470
hope, love, these three; but the greatest

00:11:03.480 --> 00:11:06.870
of these is love.'It's the most important:

00:11:06.870 --> 00:11:06.880
love.

00:11:06.880 --> 00:11:08.949
But it's not has

00:11:08.959 --> 00:11:12.470
nothing to do with prophecy as much

00:11:12.470 --> 00:11:12.480
as

00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:15.110
it's about walking in love. Faith

00:11:15.120 --> 00:11:18.470
works by love, and perfect love casteth

00:11:18.480 --> 00:11:22.269
out all fear, for fear has torment, and

00:11:22.279 --> 00:11:25.509
he that is in fear is not made

00:11:25.519 --> 00:11:27.629
perfect in love. I believe that's 1 John.

00:11:27.639 --> 00:11:31.350
I was just

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:35.829
shaking after hearing that because I

00:11:35.839 --> 00:11:39.030
realize that I haven't been there. 'There

00:11:39.040 --> 00:11:43.790
is no fear in love; but perfect love

00:11:43.790 --> 00:11:43.800
casts

00:11:43.800 --> 00:11:47.470
out fear, because fear involves torment.

00:11:47.480 --> 00:11:50.230
But he who fears has not been made

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:53.750
perfect in love. We love him because he

00:11:53.760 --> 00:11:57.110
first loved us.'So that's

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:58.949
another amazing thing:

00:11:58.959 --> 00:12:00.710
people walking in fear, walking in

00:12:00.720 --> 00:12:04.430
torment. Being perfect in love. My Father

00:12:04.440 --> 00:12:09.110
loves me, my Father died for me, he loves

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:12.910
me, he abides in me, and I refuse to fear.

00:12:12.920 --> 00:12:15.430
Perfect love casts out all fear. But I'm

00:12:15.440 --> 00:12:18.310
just saying, I look at the

00:12:18.320 --> 00:12:20.470
love scriptures, I'm looking at them and

00:12:20.480 --> 00:12:23.629
I'm meditating on them. I'm hungry for it

00:12:23.639 --> 00:12:25.590
and if this is what I'm going to do for

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:29.189
2024, it is meditate on love and get that

00:12:29.199 --> 00:12:31.230
down inside of me. Being rooted and

00:12:31.240 --> 00:12:33.150
grounded in love, being rooted and

00:12:33.160 --> 00:12:35.509
grounded in the word, getting that inside

00:12:35.519 --> 00:12:38.629
of me so that I am stable in this. Because

